						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 90 sheep for a perpetual lamp and another 30 for the supply of 30 <hi rend="italic">nāḻi</hi> of oil (ghee ?) for a special festival day in Chittirai month, in the temple of Mahādēva at Tiruppalanam in Miṟai-kūṟṟam, by one <hi rend="bold">Māṟṟamalai-Perumāṉ</hi> of Perumilaṭṭūr in Kiḻār-kūṟṟam. </p>						

